                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-1-defend50 t18080217-1-punish5"></join>
               Whipped One Hundred Yards near the East India Company's Warehouse, in the Parish of St George's in the East
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
